  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.2,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.2,
      "end": 21.92,
      "text": "영화를 통해 만나는 생생한 영어 표현"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.92,
      "end": 23.32,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.32,
      "end": 28.06,
      "text": "8월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 마이크 밀스 감독의 Come on Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.06,
      "end": 29.66,
      "text": "Come on Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.66,
      "end": 31.86,
      "text": "우리 크리스씨 오셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.6,
      "end": 33.36,
      "text": "Hello"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.36,
      "end": 34.86,
      "text": "너무 반갑고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.48,
      "end": 36.06,
      "text": "Good morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.06,
      "end": 40.08,
      "text": "권영미님께서도 반갑게 인사를 해주셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.08,
      "end": 45.74,
      "text": "한 주의 시작 월요일 아침 정현쌤 크리스쌤 목소리 들으며 시작합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.74,
      "end": 48.68,
      "text": "You know what? That's a great way to start the week"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.68,
      "end": 51.78,
      "text": "A great way to start your week"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.78,
      "end": 55.76,
      "text": "왠지 어깨가 이제 뿜뿜 솟아나는 그런 느낌이 듭니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.76,
      "end": 56.38,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.38,
      "end": 58.2,
      "text": "자부심을 가득 안고"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.2,
      "end": 60.48,
      "text": "Your shoulders are getting so high"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.48,
      "end": 66.2,
      "text": "사실 어깨가 자꾸 앞으로 굽어가지고 그게 약간 걱정거리였었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.2,
      "end": 72.06,
      "text": "이번 기회에 스트레칭을 하면서 솟아오르는 어깨를 한번 만들어 보나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.22,
      "end": 72.48,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.48,
      "end": 74.36,
      "text": "매일 뿜뿜해요 어깨를"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.36,
      "end": 74.86,
      "text": "알겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.86,
      "end": 75.88,
      "text": "좋은 습관"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.88,
      "end": 76.7,
      "text": "All right"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.7,
      "end": 80.24,
      "text": "And now we are heading to the end of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.24,
      "end": 81.86,
      "text": "Yes, the very end"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.86,
      "end": 84.52,
      "text": "예, 거의 후반부를 가고 있는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.52,
      "end": 87.52,
      "text": "우리가 아이들의 인터뷰 내용도 쫙 들어봤잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.52,
      "end": 93.1,
      "text": "인터뷰를 들으면서 굉장히 묵직한 감동들도 느껴봤습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.1,
      "end": 93.9,
      "text": "근데"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.9,
      "end": 96.6,
      "text": "But I heard something really sad happened"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.6,
      "end": 99.64,
      "text": "Yeah, one of the kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.64,
      "end": 102.96,
      "text": "You know, in this movie they have interviews with kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.96,
      "end": 105.66,
      "text": "One of the boys that was interviewed"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.66,
      "end": 108.98,
      "text": "This film is actually dedicated to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.98,
      "end": 113.28,
      "text": "And originally it was not planned to be dedicated to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.28,
      "end": 118.04,
      "text": "But a tragic, tragic accident or incident happened"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.04,
      "end": 122.58,
      "text": "He was shot and killed after this movie was filmed"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.58,
      "end": 124.64,
      "text": "In a shooting"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.64,
      "end": 126.68,
      "text": "A gun shooting"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.68,
      "end": 130.18,
      "text": "And he was from New Orleans"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.18,
      "end": 130.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.54,
      "end": 131.74,
      "text": "He lived in a neighborhood there"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.74,
      "end": 133.78,
      "text": "And they visited New Orleans"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.78,
      "end": 135.94,
      "text": "So he is one of the boys interviewed"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.94,
      "end": 140.2,
      "text": "And I liked the interview because he was really strong"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.2,
      "end": 140.62,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.62,
      "end": 143.74,
      "text": "He didn't want to reveal too much information"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.74,
      "end": 145.46,
      "text": "He said, that's my privacy"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.46,
      "end": 146.1,
      "text": "I don't need it"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.1,
      "end": 146.8,
      "text": "I don't know you"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.8,
      "end": 148.14,
      "text": "I don't need to tell you that"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.14,
      "end": 149.82,
      "text": "He was kind of cute"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.82,
      "end": 152.1,
      "text": "And he had a spunky personality"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.1,
      "end": 154.74,
      "text": "So I was saddened to hear that"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.74,
      "end": 156.36,
      "text": "He was killed in a shooting"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.36,
      "end": 158.0,
      "text": "After the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.0,
      "end": 158.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.42,
      "end": 158.5,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.5,
      "end": 167.2,
      "text": "He was killed in a shooting"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.2,
      "end": 168.1,
      "text": "A shooting"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.1,
      "end": 170.04,
      "text": "Yeah, shootings are a big problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.04,
      "end": 170.36,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.36,
      "end": 172.9,
      "text": "And before his 10th birthday"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.9,
      "end": 174.98,
      "text": "One month before his 10th birthday"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.98,
      "end": 177.12,
      "text": "In front of his own house"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.12,
      "end": 179.24,
      "text": "He was shot and killed"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.24,
      "end": 183.38,
      "text": "So the director decided to dedicate the movie to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.38,
      "end": 186.78,
      "text": "And if you watch at the end of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.78,
      "end": 189.08,
      "text": "Before the, or during the end credits"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.08,
      "end": 192.18,
      "text": "There is a dedication card"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.18,
      "end": 193.94,
      "text": "A little card that comes out"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.94,
      "end": 195.16,
      "text": "That is blue"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.16,
      "end": 197.74,
      "text": "Which was his favorite color"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.74,
      "end": 200.06,
      "text": "So it's significant"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.06,
      "end": 202.04,
      "text": "And it's an honor of him"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.04,
      "end": 205.72,
      "text": "특별히 이 영화가 블랙 앤 와이트 film이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.72,
      "end": 206.82,
      "text": "그럼에도 불구하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.82,
      "end": 209.78,
      "text": "이 어린아이를 추모하는 의미로"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.78,
      "end": 210.86,
      "text": "이 부분만"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.86,
      "end": 213.66,
      "text": "이제 블루 칼라로 적혀 있었다고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.66,
      "end": 215.52,
      "text": "The only color in the whole movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.52,
      "end": 217.04,
      "text": "So sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.04,
      "end": 219.56,
      "text": "이제 오늘 준비된 장면 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.56,
      "end": 223.54,
      "text": "Do you think that the world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.04,
      "end": 226.88,
      "text": "No, nothing's really that fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.88,
      "end": 228.82,
      "text": "There's always going to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.82,
      "end": 230.82,
      "text": "Like, probably going to be more war"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.82,
      "end": 233.46,
      "text": "Since there's more things to fight about"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.46,
      "end": 234.6,
      "text": "If you keep on building"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.6,
      "end": 237.32,
      "text": "On to what's in the past"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.32,
      "end": 241.0,
      "text": "What causes flooding within yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.0,
      "end": 242.5,
      "text": "Within, whether it's in your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.5,
      "end": 243.3,
      "text": "Within your heart"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.3,
      "end": 244.48,
      "text": "Within your spirit"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.48,
      "end": 246.18,
      "text": "What causes flooding"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.18,
      "end": 247.98,
      "text": "Within you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.88,
      "end": 253.7,
      "text": "I think it would be like"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.7,
      "end": 256.16,
      "text": "Not, like, feeling that"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.16,
      "end": 258.26,
      "text": "Like I said, no one cares"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.26,
      "end": 259.66,
      "text": "Or like, just feeling that"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.66,
      "end": 260.7,
      "text": "I'm like, alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.7,
      "end": 261.48,
      "text": "Sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.48,
      "end": 265.68,
      "text": "It's an interview in New Orleans"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.68,
      "end": 267.56,
      "text": "아까 들으신 것처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.56,
      "end": 269.36,
      "text": "New Orleans으로 넘어와서"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.36,
      "end": 272.24,
      "text": "계속 진행이 되는 인터뷰의 한 장면이었고"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.24,
      "end": 275.72,
      "text": "어린이들이 인터뷰를 하고 있다는 것이"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.72,
      "end": 277.12,
      "text": "공통적이긴 한데"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.12,
      "end": 281.08,
      "text": "약간 어느 도시에 사느냐에 따라서"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.08,
      "end": 284.92,
      "text": "It seems that the children have quite different characteristics"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.92,
      "end": 286.9,
      "text": "From a region to a region"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.9,
      "end": 288.06,
      "text": "Different cities"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.06,
      "end": 290.0,
      "text": "Different parts of the US"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.0,
      "end": 292.38,
      "text": "Which is like many countries"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.38,
      "end": 293.52,
      "text": "All in one"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.52,
      "end": 296.62,
      "text": "So, yeah, they have different life experiences"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.62,
      "end": 299.34,
      "text": "But their answers are all very raw"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.34,
      "end": 300.58,
      "text": "Sincer"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.58,
      "end": 302.18,
      "text": "Very authentic"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.18,
      "end": 305.54,
      "text": "굉장히 심도 깊은 대답을 들을 수가 있었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.54,
      "end": 309.54,
      "text": "그럼 주요 표현은 어떤 게 있었을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.76,
      "end": 310.86,
      "text": "The world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.2,
      "end": 312.76,
      "text": "The world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.18,
      "end": 315.92,
      "text": "이렇게 끝부분을 올리면서 이야기를 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.92,
      "end": 319.26,
      "text": "그러면 의문문처럼 생각을 하셔야 되는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.26,
      "end": 320.06,
      "text": "I ask the question"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.06,
      "end": 321.42,
      "text": "Is the world fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.6,
      "end": 322.38,
      "text": "I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.38,
      "end": 323.5,
      "text": "Nothing's fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.5,
      "end": 324.84,
      "text": "Life's not fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.84,
      "end": 325.32,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.32,
      "end": 329.0,
      "text": "인생은 불공평하다라고 생각이 될 때도 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.0,
      "end": 329.52,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.52,
      "end": 330.9,
      "text": "The world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.14,
      "end": 332.74,
      "text": "세상이 공정한가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.71,
      "end": 335.59,
      "text": "Keep on building onto"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.59,
      "end": 338.05,
      "text": "Keep on ing"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.05,
      "end": 340.33,
      "text": "이런 구조로 많이 외워보셨을 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.33,
      "end": 342.37,
      "text": "뭐뭐를 계속하다라는 건데"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.37,
      "end": 344.19,
      "text": "Building onto"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.19,
      "end": 345.07,
      "text": "라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.07,
      "end": 349.59,
      "text": "뭐뭐 위에 쌓는 것을 계속하다라고 해석하시면 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.59,
      "end": 352.99,
      "text": "What causes flooding within yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.47,
      "end": 354.85,
      "text": "That's a deep question"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.85,
      "end": 355.27,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.27,
      "end": 359.59,
      "text": "굉장히 비유적으로 질문을 하고 있는 상황에서 들렸습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.59,
      "end": 362.67,
      "text": "What causes flooding within yourself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.27,
      "end": 364.93,
      "text": "당신 자신 안에"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.93,
      "end": 366.67,
      "text": "What causes flooding?"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.89,
      "end": 367.49,
      "text": "이라고 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.49,
      "end": 370.03,
      "text": "F-L-O-O-D-I-N-G"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.03,
      "end": 371.03,
      "text": "라는 철자이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.03,
      "end": 373.33,
      "text": "홍수를 일으키는 것?"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.69,
      "end": 374.09,
      "text": "이거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.09,
      "end": 375.23,
      "text": "어떨 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.23,
      "end": 380.37,
      "text": "당신 안에 감정이 크게 일렁이냐라는 질문으로 해석하시면 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.37,
      "end": 381.73,
      "text": "Ah, good or bad"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.73,
      "end": 382.75,
      "text": "It doesn't matter"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.75,
      "end": 384.05,
      "text": "음, 아마도요"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.05,
      "end": 386.39,
      "text": "What causes a flooding of emotion"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.39,
      "end": 387.85,
      "text": "inside you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.15,
      "end": 389.55,
      "text": "It could be good, could be bad"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.55,
      "end": 390.19,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.19,
      "end": 393.89,
      "text": "어떤 상황이냐에 따라서 달라질 수 있을 것 같기는 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.89,
      "end": 396.57,
      "text": "그럼 이 표현들 기억하시면서 다시 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.57,
      "end": 400.52,
      "text": "Do you think that the world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.04,
      "end": 401.26,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.26,
      "end": 403.88,
      "text": "Nothing's really that fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.88,
      "end": 405.82,
      "text": "There's always going to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.82,
      "end": 407.84,
      "text": "like probably going to be more war"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.84,
      "end": 410.46,
      "text": "since there's more things to fight about"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.46,
      "end": 411.66,
      "text": "if you keep on building"
    },
    {
      "start": 411.66,
      "end": 414.32,
      "text": "onto what's in the past"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.32,
      "end": 418.0,
      "text": "What causes flooding within yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.0,
      "end": 419.5,
      "text": "within whether it's in your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.5,
      "end": 420.32,
      "text": "within your heart"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.32,
      "end": 421.5,
      "text": "within your spirit"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.5,
      "end": 425.0,
      "text": "What causes flooding of within you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.23,
      "end": 430.69,
      "text": "Um, I think it would be like"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.69,
      "end": 433.15,
      "text": "not like feeling that"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.15,
      "end": 435.25,
      "text": "like I said, no one cares"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.25,
      "end": 436.65,
      "text": "or like just feeling that"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.65,
      "end": 438.53,
      "text": "I'm like alone sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.53,
      "end": 444.14,
      "text": "Wow, 질문들이 굉장히 hard to answer"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.14,
      "end": 447.28,
      "text": "Yeah, how would you answer this question"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.28,
      "end": 448.8,
      "text": "if you mind me asking?"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.14,
      "end": 449.66,
      "text": "조샘?"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.8,
      "end": 452.56,
      "text": "아니요, 저도 이거 정말 쉽게 대답 못할 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.56,
      "end": 454.32,
      "text": "Do you think that the world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.58,
      "end": 455.52,
      "text": "Oh, not actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.52,
      "end": 456.46,
      "text": "No?"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.86,
      "end": 457.46,
      "text": "Oh, no"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.46,
      "end": 459.06,
      "text": "Yeah, sometimes unfair"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.06,
      "end": 463.62,
      "text": "Yeah, 아마도 공정하다라고 생각이 들 때도 있지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.62,
      "end": 465.8,
      "text": "불공정하다라고 생각이 드는 경우도"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.8,
      "end": 467.06,
      "text": "꽤 많이 있을 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.06,
      "end": 467.74,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.74,
      "end": 470.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm trying to"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.0,
      "end": 471.4,
      "text": "I mean, growing up"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.4,
      "end": 472.38,
      "text": "you learn"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.38,
      "end": 473.86,
      "text": "or you try to learn"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.86,
      "end": 476.1,
      "text": "I still can't accept it"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.1,
      "end": 476.62,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.62,
      "end": 479.9,
      "text": "심지어 우리가 이렇게 영화 장면을 들여다보면서도"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.9,
      "end": 481.66,
      "text": "매일매일 배우는 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.66,
      "end": 483.66,
      "text": "You can learn from everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.66,
      "end": 484.68,
      "text": "From everyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.68,
      "end": 485.5,
      "text": "and everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.5,
      "end": 486.64,
      "text": "There's always something to learn"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.64,
      "end": 488.04,
      "text": "Life is not fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.04,
      "end": 488.84,
      "text": "태도입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.84,
      "end": 492.07,
      "text": "자, 조니가 질문을 뭐라고 했죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.29,
      "end": 494.41,
      "text": "Do you think that the world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.59,
      "end": 495.95,
      "text": "아하, 첫 번째로"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.95,
      "end": 499.47,
      "text": "주요 표현에서 점검을 해본 구조가"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.47,
      "end": 500.95,
      "text": "여기에서 활용이 되었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.95,
      "end": 504.57,
      "text": "결국엔 간접 의문문에서 활용이 되었네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.57,
      "end": 507.03,
      "text": "Do you think that the world is fair?"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.03,
      "end": 509.53,
      "text": "세상이 공정하다고 생각해?"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.37,
      "end": 512.45,
      "text": "No, nothing's really that fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.45,
      "end": 514.35,
      "text": "I like that answer"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.35,
      "end": 514.77,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.77,
      "end": 517.55,
      "text": "어린이 한 명이 이렇게 대답을 한 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.55,
      "end": 519.97,
      "text": "No, nothing's really that fair"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.97,
      "end": 521.03,
      "text": "아니요"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.03,
      "end": 524.33,
      "text": "아무것도 그렇게 공정한 거는 없어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.33,
      "end": 526.87,
      "text": "그러니까 공정한 건 없다고 생각해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.87,
      "end": 528.65,
      "text": "There's always gonna be a"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.65,
      "end": 530.63,
      "text": "like probably gonna be more war"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.63,
      "end": 533.07,
      "text": "since there's more things to fight about"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.07,
      "end": 536.35,
      "text": "if you keep on building onto what's in the past"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.35,
      "end": 539.19,
      "text": "우와, 대답이 엄청납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.19,
      "end": 540.39,
      "text": "한번 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.39,
      "end": 540.65,
      "text": "It is"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.65,
      "end": 541.81,
      "text": "들을수록 엄청나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.81,
      "end": 542.69,
      "text": "생각할수록"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.69,
      "end": 542.95,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.95,
      "end": 545.05,
      "text": "There's always gonna be a"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.05,
      "end": 547.33,
      "text": "like probably gonna be more war"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.33,
      "end": 548.83,
      "text": "이 부분 먼저 해석을 해보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.83,
      "end": 552.83,
      "text": "전쟁은 아마도 gonna be more"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.83,
      "end": 553.51,
      "text": "이라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.51,
      "end": 555.27,
      "text": "더 늘어날 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.27,
      "end": 556.21,
      "text": "라는 거고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.21,
      "end": 559.35,
      "text": "Since there's more things to fight about"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.35,
      "end": 562.31,
      "text": "싸울 것들이 늘어나니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.31,
      "end": 563.19,
      "text": "라는 건데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.19,
      "end": 565.59,
      "text": "뭐에 대해서 싸울 것들이 늘어나냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.59,
      "end": 569.95,
      "text": "If you keep on building onto what's in the past"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.95,
      "end": 570.77,
      "text": "라고 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.77,
      "end": 573.79,
      "text": "과거를 덮어두고"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.79,
      "end": 575.47,
      "text": "그 위로 쌓기만 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.47,
      "end": 576.07,
      "text": "이라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.07,
      "end": 577.73,
      "text": "That is deep"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.73,
      "end": 579.33,
      "text": "Like grudges"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.33,
      "end": 580.57,
      "text": "old fights"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.57,
      "end": 582.43,
      "text": "If you don't resolve them"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.43,
      "end": 584.61,
      "text": "If you don't forgive the other person"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.61,
      "end": 586.75,
      "text": "you just keep building onto that"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.75,
      "end": 587.85,
      "text": "bad feeling"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.85,
      "end": 589.27,
      "text": "and building and building"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.27,
      "end": 590.85,
      "text": "뒤끝 없게"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.85,
      "end": 593.21,
      "text": "한 번에 상쇄를 시키면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.21,
      "end": 595.07,
      "text": "해결을 해나가야 된다는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.07,
      "end": 598.05,
      "text": "네, 뒤끝 있는 사람들 많다는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.05,
      "end": 599.93,
      "text": "그래서 war 계속 있다는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.93,
      "end": 600.89,
      "text": "이 어린아이가"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.89,
      "end": 602.01,
      "text": "그 기특한 생각"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.01,
      "end": 602.95,
      "text": "엄청나게"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.95,
      "end": 604.35,
      "text": "현명한 생각입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.35,
      "end": 606.31,
      "text": "과거에 있었던 일 위에"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.31,
      "end": 606.89,
      "text": "자꾸자꾸"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.89,
      "end": 608.03,
      "text": "쌓아놓기만 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.03,
      "end": 609.81,
      "text": "싸울 것들이 늘어나니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.81,
      "end": 612.03,
      "text": "전쟁은 아마도 더 늘어날 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.03,
      "end": 613.23,
      "text": "라는 대답이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.23,
      "end": 614.19,
      "text": "하루살이 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.19,
      "end": 615.25,
      "text": "전쟁은 없겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.25,
      "end": 615.91,
      "text": "하루살이"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.91,
      "end": 616.95,
      "text": "forget everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.95,
      "end": 617.71,
      "text": "For example"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.71,
      "end": 619.49,
      "text": "제가 가끔 그런 생각이 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.49,
      "end": 619.99,
      "text": "아, 진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.99,
      "end": 621.71,
      "text": "Today, I have one day"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.71,
      "end": 623.59,
      "text": "and then I reset"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.59,
      "end": 624.71,
      "text": "go to sleep, reset"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.71,
      "end": 626.21,
      "text": "wash my brain"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.21,
      "end": 627.51,
      "text": "I'm brand new"
